      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, functional option for daily commuting. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car shows clear signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches on the exterior and some thinning paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some minor staining and wear consistent with regular use. It has been maintained regularly, though it will likely require some minor suspension work in the near future. This is an honest, high-mileage driver that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
