    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner! Whether you're just ziping around town or planning a longer trip, this beauty is super reliable and runs like a charm. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 34500.0,
